  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0db4\u0dba\u0ddd\u0da2\u0db1\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dc5\u0dcf\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dbb 36\u0d9a \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "36 years in prison for abusing a girl",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Hambantota High Court Judge Mr. Priyantha Liyanage sentenced a person who sexually abused a 12-year-old girl in Agunukolapalassa 12 years ago to 36 years of hard labor.",
        "In addition to the prison sentence, the judge ordered a fine of 30,000 rupees and compensation of 03 lakh rupees to the victim girl.",
        "It was said in the court that a 12-year-old girl had been deceived and abused on several occasions.",
        "Accordingly, in the long hearing held by the prosecution, the 04 charges against the accused were proved beyond reasonable doubt by the High Court Judge Priyantha Liyanage, who sentenced the accused.",
        "Mr. Nimantha Jayawickrama, who appeared in court on behalf of the Attorney General, said that the victim girl was 12 years old at the time of the incident, and the accused was 29 years old. According to this, the society also looks forward to the punishment given to an accused person in such crimes. It was requested to give a severe punishment that would set an example to other people in the society.",
        "Accordingly, Hambantota High Court Judge Priyantha Liyanage sentenced the accused to 04 years imprisonment with 08 years hard labor for charges 1 and 3 and a fine of 5000 rupees each and 10,000 rupees for the two related charges.",
        "In case of non-payment of fine, 06 months imprisonment was also imposed. Also, for charges 02 and 04, a prison sentence of 14 years to 28 years was imposed and a fine of 10,000 rupees and 20,000 rupees was also imposed for those two charges. If the fine is not paid, a prison sentence of 01 year for two years was also imposed. Apart from this, it was also ordered to pay a compensation of Rs."
      ],
